tGenerator:\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md:1255:1. Sends the lesson to the LLM asking it to generate a checker script\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1256-2. Parses the response as JSON with `path` and `content` fields\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1257-3. Creates parent directories if needed\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1258-4. Writes the script file with executable permissions (0755)\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1259-5. For agent-type steps, generates a prompt file instead\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1260-\n--\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1265-\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1266-**Step 5: Commit**\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1267-\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1268-```bash\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1269-git add internal/evolution/\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md:1270:git commit -m \"feat(evolution): add Script Generator for new checker steps\"\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1271-```\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1272-\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1273----\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1274-\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1275-## Task 14: DSL Mutator (Branch C)\n--\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-50-                    └──────────────┬──────────────────────┘\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-51-                                   │\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-52-              ┌────────────────────┼────────