{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_014PU4J94aZyKeuURBiZ9UnN","type":"tool_result","content":"   231→#### Branch B: Script Generator (LLM)\n   232→\n   233→Handles `new_step` lessons where step_type is \"script\" or \"agent\".\n   234→\n   235→- Receives the lesson describing what check or analysis is needed\n   236→- Generates a script file (shell, Python, etc.) implementing the check, or a\n   237→  prompt file for agent steps\n   238→- Script/prompt is written to the project directory (e.g.,\n   239→  `scripts/security-scan.sh` or `prompts/review.md`)\n   240→- Output: the file path and content\n   241→\n   242→#### Branch C: DSL Mutator (deterministic Go code)\n   243→\n   244→Handles structural workflow changes. Receives structured proposals and applies\n   245→them to the `.cloche` workflow file. Four operations:\n   246→\n   247→**Add Step Definition:**\n   248→```json\n   249→{\n   250→  \"op\": \"add_step\",\n   251→  \"name\": \"security-scan\",\n   252→  \"type\": \"script\",\n   253→  \"config\": {\n   254→    \"run\": \"gosec ./...\",\n   255→    \"results\": [\"success\", \"fail\"]\n   256→  }\n   257→}\n   258→```\n   259→\n   260→Parses the workflow file, inserts the step definition, serializes back."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e576fc45-fcda-491a-aa5c-2d5791efc9e9","uuid":"b05b610f-dd8f-4352-a42e-a476cb5b01df","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md","content":"#### Branch B: Script Generator (LLM)\n\nHandles `new_step` lessons where step_type is \"script\" or \"agent\".\n\n- Receives the lesson describing what check or analysis is needed\n- Generates a script file (shell, Python, etc.) implementing the check, or a\n  prompt file for agent steps\n- Script/prompt is written to the project directory (e.g.,\n  `scripts/security-scan.sh` or `prompts/review.md`)\n- Output: the file path and content\n\n#### Branch C: DSL Mutator (deterministic Go code)\n\nHandles structural workflow changes. Receives structured proposals and applies\nthem to the `.cloche` workflow file. Four operations:\n\n**Add Step Definition:**\n```json\n{\n  \"op\": \"add_step\",\n  \"name\": \"security-scan\",\n  \"type\": \"script\",\n  \"config\": {\n    \"run\": \"gosec ./...\",\n    \"results\": [\"success\", \"fail\"]\n  }\n}\n```\n\nParses the workflow file, inserts the step definition, serializes back.","numLines":30,"startLine":231,"totalLines":449}}}
